Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你「抢镜头」这话算什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.90,subtitle_16,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,204)}压岁钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.65,0:00:11.90,subtitle_16,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(346,431)}其①
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.78,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千岁 给你压岁钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.17,0:00:16.91,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也帮我把千早的给她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:19.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇~ 阿姨 谢谢~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:22.04,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千早 可能你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.17,0:00:24.92,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听说今年开始 十岁以上的人就不能收压岁钱了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:27.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说制订了这么一条法律呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.36,0:00:31.67,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,千岁! 你这孩子!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:34.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用两个人的压岁钱来买贵衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:36.02,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是为了两年后的千早哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:39.56,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H165051&\an7\frz280.008\pos(117,122)}哎…\N今年开始\N拿不到压岁钱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.05,0:00:39.56,writings3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(804,348)}千早的衣服100%是别人穿旧的。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.06,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H165051&\an7\frz280.008\pos(117,122)\blur8}哎…\N今年开始\N拿不到压岁钱了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.06,writings3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(804,348)\blur8}千早的衣服100%是别人穿旧的。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.06,subtitle_16,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,204)}压岁钱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.56,0:00:42.06,subtitle_16,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(346,431)}其②
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.52,0:00:42.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 在帮杂志拍照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.69,0:00:46.63,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模特真好啊 总是能穿上名牌的新款式
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.47,0:00:49.83,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算没穿名牌的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.03,0:00:51.43,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也还是姐姐更漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.61,0:00:56.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个真的可以给我吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明才刚买的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:59.70,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦 反正我会让人再买给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:00.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:04.46,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(717,114)\frz288.001}姐姐不仅漂亮\N还很温柔!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.94,0:01:04.46,writings3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,461)\frz6.526}贪掉千早的压岁钱买的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.96,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\pos(717,114)\frz288.001\blur8}姐姐不仅漂亮\N还很温柔!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.96,writings3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(460,461)\frz6.526\blur8}贪掉千早的压岁钱买的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.96,subtitle_16,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(432,204)}压岁钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.96,subtitle_16,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(346,431)}其③
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说 你拿到多少压岁钱了?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:09.84,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真岛应该有很多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.63,0:01:12.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绵谷你拿到多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:13.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.84,0:01:16.36,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十岁以上的人收圣诞礼物和压岁钱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:18.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,法律是不允许的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.30,0:01:18.59,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz285.015\pos(211,296)\c&H172E20&}妈妈说的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:20.52,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你傻啊 那怎么可…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.56,0:01:21.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 太一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.34,0:01:23.08,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十岁以后就不能拿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.11,0:01:25.32,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,违法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.21,0:01:27.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.24,0:01:29.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:31.57,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其他人也拿到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:32.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.18,0:01:32.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:35.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说回来 真岛拿了多少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.09,0:01:35.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.11,0:01:36.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:38.64,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,十一万五千日元吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.20,0:01:43.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,违法!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:44.26,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯罪!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.38,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H313E45&\pos(765,197)\frz260.045}怎么可能有拿那么多的\N孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.38,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H313E45&\frz278.939\pos(406,72)}那是他爸爸的\N年终奖数额啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.37,0:01:52.38,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\c&H313E45&\pos(215,145)\frz290.84}原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.38,0:01:52.38,subtitle_16_end,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(856,578)}压岁钱 完
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.76,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能拿到那么多嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.95,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是他爸爸的年终奖数额吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.42,0:01:57.43,title_text,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fad(864,897)\pos(490,291)}红叶漫小仓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:02.15,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 这不就是百人一首吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:04.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绫濑同学你会这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.78,0:02:06.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要说会不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.34,0:02:08.69,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们学校每年都会举办歌留多大赛的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.70,0:02:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们来比吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:11.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.98,0:02:13.75,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以是可以 但是没有人来读啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:16.21,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有磁带啊 磁带
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:20.35,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…怎么弄来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:24.11,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把25张牌分成三段排好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.39,0:02:29.88,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到上句读出来 就要拿掉写有对应下句的牌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.60,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦 就是个歌留多比赛而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:40.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种眼神…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:43.03,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以开始了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.97,0:02:45.55,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.54,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「秋来…」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.07,0:02:53.54,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,あらしふく…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:58.72,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多…以前是这样玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.46,0:03:02.06,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少要抢到一张
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:07.89,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那张牌的上句我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:11.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是「激流戏浅水 岩前两纷飞」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:11.34,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,658)}せをはやみ　いはにせかるる　たきがはの
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.64,0:03:14.12,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,至少要抢到那一张…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.35,0:03:16.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有那一张…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.07,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,せ…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「激…」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.10,0:03:27.97,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老师!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.04,0:03:34.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可以代替绵谷同学比赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.80,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是无所谓的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.34,0:03:38.18,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正千早绝对更弱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:41.41,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代替绵谷同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对要赢!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:45.31,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:52.05,waka,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}しろきをみれば　よぞふけにける
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.88,0:03:52.05,note,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「更深乌啼晚 繁霜满清霄」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.68,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是「代替」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.42,0:03:49.20,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是「我」…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:52.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我个人要赢过太一!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:04:01.17,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和太一的比赛 我觉得非常有意思!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.77,0:04:05.34,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多太好玩了!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:09.87,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 和绵谷同学比赛的时候就不是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:12.09,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他可是要成为名人的人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.48,0:04:15.23,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 绫濑同学就是女王咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:17.71,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.40,0:04:22.05,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是女生中间 最强的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.10,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女王…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.53,0:05:49.37,writings3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(1000,0)}店长不在的时候 其实有偷偷看过的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.37,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H273E35&\frz284.981\move(1038,366,1026,345,0,484)}看透你的啦\N新
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.47,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用四字熟语描述一下对朋友的印象吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}类似汉语的成语
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「天衣无缝」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:52.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}天衣无缝（日语）：不做作，非常天真自然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.78,0:05:54.00,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎 什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.18,0:05:56.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那肉包小子就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:57.44,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「烤肉套餐（大份）」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.44,0:05:58.19,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.47,0:05:59.50,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么驹野说白了就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:00.45,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「情报收集」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:05:59.51,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\frz297.672\pos(-4,362)}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:05:59.51,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(48,453)\frz18.92}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:05:59.55,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\frz297.672\pos(235,362)}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.51,0:05:59.55,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(287,453)\frz18.92}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:03.38,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\frz297.672\pos(330,362)}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:03.38,writings2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs35\pos(382,453)\frz18.92}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:01.29,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.46,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个说的都不是四字熟语吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.82,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小奏给人的印象是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「诗歌管弦」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.07,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}诗歌管弦（日语）：既懂汉诗与和歌，又懂乐器\N引申为文学和音乐都拿手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:06.10,writings3,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.015\pos(186,499)}{\alpha&HE5}哦——
